'''Great Scott''' may refer to:

*"Great Scott!", an exclamation of surprise or amazement which was commonly found in [[superhero]] [[comic books]] and often said by [[Superman]]; it is also known as a line from the character [[Doctor Emmett Brown|Doc Brown]] of the ''[[Back to the Future trilogy|Back to the Future]]'' film trilogy. A possible origin of the phrase is that people seeking to emulate the German [[Prince Albert]] altered and anglicized "Greuss Gott!", or "Good God!" into "Great Scott!".
*[[Great Scott (club)|Great Scott]], a live music venue in [[Allston]], [[Massachusetts]].
*[[John Schweigert]], an ex-[[professional wrestling|professional wrestler]] known as The Great Scott
*Great Scott (band) formed in 2005 from Saint John, New Brunswick, Canada.

